# Créer le fichier .gitignore
echo. > .gitignore
```

Contenu de `.gitignore` :
```
# Python
backend/venv/
backend/__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
backend/db.sqlite3
backend/*.log
backend/media/
backend/staticfiles/

# Node.js
realtime/node_modules/
frontend/node_modules/
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Environment files
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# Build files
frontend/dist/
frontend/build/

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
```

---

